Required Files
Sec-4B model: https://huggingface.co/OpenIXCLab/SeC-4B
Note: this is very large, and if you haven't pre-downloaded this auto-download will take a while depending on your connection speed.

Required non-standard nodes for this workflow
Comfyui-SecNodes: https://github.com/9nate-drake/Comfyui-SecNodes

This is a memory heavy model. To reduce memory use:
* offload video to cpu (negligible speed penalty and large vram usage reduction)
* lower 'mllm_memory_size' (number of frames the llm is using as context. very small vram usage reduction)


Inputs
Annotation Frame: the frame that has the best representation of what you want to segment
Tracking Direction: Which direction to segment from your annotation frame
